bios:
	do we have the latest bios?
	upgrade from win before reinstall
	(or do from another win disk swapped in)

battery:
	sysctl hw: batter condition?

disk:
	replace rotating disks with ssd or nvme
	can we boot from nvme?

video:
	video(1): does the internal webcam work?
	xvinfo: do we have a Xv adapter

cpu C states:
	do we have at least C3?

suspend/resume:
	does everything wake up correctly?
	including wifi?

audio:
	does the internal mic work
	do the internal speakers work?
	does the headphone jack work?
	do headphones mute the speakers?
	do volume and mute buttons work?
	sndioctl, mixerctl, audioctl

wifi:
	is the card supported? (Replace with athn or iwn.)
	https://marc.info/?l=openbsd-misc&m=160278763201347&w=2
	https://marc.info/?l=openbsd-misc&m=149079257620166&w=2

report:
	dmesg
	acpidump
	sysctl hw
	pcidump
	usbdevs
	usbutils
	xdpyinfo
	xvinfo
	mixerctl
